  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/9bbf96f37bc0788bdb93ec6e46ea0e6a.poster.avif?t=1730487672\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/9bbf96f37bc0788bdb93ec6e46ea0e6a.webm?t=1730487672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/9bbf96f37bc0788bdb93ec6e46ea0e6a.mp4?t=1730487672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/b76b3d2e31f11bc377ed7249f0b4d020.webp?t=1730487672\" width=600 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to the Valley of Shadow.</strong> In it, you will experience a REAL harrowing journey of loss through the eyes of the developer. Experience the depth of grief as he visits the places of his childhood and discovers where love and acceptance come together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/8cc15598b610a6dc5a58598b3cd83af1.webp?t=1730487672\" width=600 height=61 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/c34f048bb91f796ef403abd4efc0de9f.poster.avif?t=1730487672\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/c34f048bb91f796ef403abd4efc0de9f.webm?t=1730487672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/c34f048bb91f796ef403abd4efc0de9f.mp4?t=1730487672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/60295fad026bc4069e95053a6cf60dd0.avif?t=1730487672\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the dramatic retelling of a traumatic event in the lives of the developers, three siblings, through the eyes of one as he attempts to heal. REAL VHS tapes, photographs and answering machine audio piece together the fall and redemption of a once broken family.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/3b2661648d5627980cda1c36bd2f2fb5.webp?t=1730487672\" width=600 height=61 /></span><br><br>Unlock some of the most iconic magical abilities from the fantasy genre as you make your way through the Valley and beyond: Light, Force Missile, and Fireball. Engage in increasingly complex challenges that require a mastery of each spell, both individually and in conjunction with the others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/291ff1434db90769db1fa4af744003fe.poster.avif?t=1730487672\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/291ff1434db90769db1fa4af744003fe.webm?t=1730487672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/291ff1434db90769db1fa4af744003fe.mp4?t=1730487672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/7bf0181892c0673968161d08fc303a28.webp?t=1730487672\" width=600 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cast Light</strong> to not only find your way around dark areas, but also solve mind-bending puzzles revolving around Light & Shadow. Strategically manipulate your environment to control the shadows indirectly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/90c5afda3183cb67f5e2a683ade803ec.poster.avif?t=1730487672\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/90c5afda3183cb67f5e2a683ade803ec.webm?t=1730487672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/90c5afda3183cb67f5e2a683ade803ec.mp4?t=1730487672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/415c1f494c08d5f0456a65df1f51edfc.webp?t=1730487672\" width=600 height=31 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Force Missiles</strong> always find their target, but <i>which</i> target is up to you. Destroy obstacles, manipulate the environment, and reposition yourself to control the route that your missiles take.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/51635e8a84f849c93b8f53e88d3efd3a.poster.avif?t=1730487672\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/51635e8a84f849c93b8f53e88d3efd3a.webm?t=1730487672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/51635e8a84f849c93b8f53e88d3efd3a.mp4?t=1730487672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/12f2664eefc50236c50cb83aa3b2a176.webp?t=1730487672\" width=600 height=34 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fireball</strong> opens new avenues to explore while you progress deeper into the icy cold Valley of Shadow. Carve through ice to make a path for Force Missile, or melt snow to shine Light on the other side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/6bcd04194084ef44804e40980df5e7fa.webp?t=1730487672\" width=600 height=61 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/81dfd661d1097e96f8b3b3fc3f20df36.poster.avif?t=1730487672\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/81dfd661d1097e96f8b3b3fc3f20df36.webm?t=1730487672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/81dfd661d1097e96f8b3b3fc3f20df36.mp4?t=1730487672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/b13aa0640874d928e8778b8160d79c9a.webp?t=1730487672\" width=600 height=33 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Valley of Shadow is both a treasure and a tomb of nostalgia from the 80's, 90's and the 2000's. Each piece is significant, and each one familiar to the player. Some of the most popular pieces even have their own puzzles designed for them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/022f2e5749afee4f053b13266432ff0d.poster.avif?t=1730487672\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/022f2e5749afee4f053b13266432ff0d.webm?t=1730487672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/022f2e5749afee4f053b13266432ff0d.mp4?t=1730487672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
